A fish stall is a stall, requiring 42 Thieving to steal from, yielding 42 Thieving experience and one of the following items: raw salmon, raw tuna or raw lobster. It can be stolen from every 15 ticks (9 seconds). The fishmonger or fish monger will not trade with the player if they have stolen from the stall in the last 15 minutes.

The stalls in Rellekka require completion of The Fremennik Trials quest. Thieving from the Miscellania fish stalls lowers approval rating in Managing Miscellania, however the Etceteria stall does not lower rating. The stall in The Warrens has a level 21 Thief, instead of a guard, nearby attacks they can see the player attempt to steal from the stall.
